    "description": "<p>You see how it will come. You see how it could be prevented. Both are you.</p><p>Your body sharpens and hones itself into the tool necessary to make the choice. <strong>You die</strong>. If you are returned to life, you may now wield this tool: the <strong>Endbringer</strong>. If not, someone else takes it and receives the rest of this ability. Describe what the perfect weapon, made of your body, looks like.</p><p>When anyone wields the Endbringer as a weapon, even minor contact with it will kill any mundane or Anomalous target in a dramatic and unignorable way that will create 7 Loose Ends if seen by even one person.</p><p>Every time you use it, mark out one space on <strong>The End</strong> track. When the track is full, go to <strong>J4</strong>.</p>",
